<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>scellrun — full pipeline report</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; max-width: 1080px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; color: #222; line-height: 1.55; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.7rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; padding-bottom: .3rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 2.2rem; padding-bottom: .15rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  h3 { font-size: 1rem; color: #555; margin-top: 1.4rem; }
  a { color: #1f4e8a; }
  .stage-card { padding: .8rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #e6e6e6; border-radius: .4rem; margin: .8rem 0; background: #fafafa; }
  .stage-card.absent { opacity: .55; background: #f3f3f3; }
  .pill { display: inline-block; padding: .1rem .55rem; border-radius: .8rem; background: #eef4ff; color: #1f4e8a; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .pill.absent { background: #eee; color: #888; }
  table.runs { font-size: .88rem; width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  table.runs th, table.runs td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: .3rem .5rem; text-align: left; }
  table.runs th { background: #f6f6f6; }
  code { background: #f0f0f0; padding: .05rem .3rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: .9em; }
  ul.artifacts { list-style: square; padding-left: 1.2rem; font-size: .9rem; }
  .provenance { background: #fafaf6; border-left: 3px solid #c7b07a; padding: .6rem .9rem; margin: .8rem 0 1.2rem; font-size: .92rem; color: #555; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>scellrun — full pipeline report</h1>

<p style="color:#666;">
  Run directory: <code>{{ run_dir }}</code>
</p>

<h2>Stages</h2>
{% for stage in stages %}
<div class="stage-card {% if not stage.present %}absent{% endif %}">
  <div>
    <span class="pill {% if not stage.present %}absent{% endif %}">{{ loop.index0 + 1 }}. {{ stage.name }}</span>
    {% if stage.present %}
      <span style="font-size:.85rem; color:#555;">→ <code>{{ stage.dir_name }}/</code></span>
      {% if stage.report_path %}
        — <a href="../{{ stage.dir_name }}/report.html">open report.html</a>
      {% endif %}
    {% else %}
      <span style="font-size:.85rem; color:#999;">(not run)</span>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% if stage.present and stage.artifacts %}
  <ul class="artifacts">
    {% for name, path in stage.artifacts.items() %}
      <li><a href="../{{ stage.dir_name }}/{{ name }}">{{ name }}</a></li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% endif %}
</div>
{% endfor %}

<h2>Run manifest (chronological)</h2>
{% if manifest.stages %}
<table class="runs">
  <thead>
    <tr><th>#</th><th>command</th><th>ran at</th><th>key params</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for s in manifest.stages %}
    <tr>
      <td>{{ loop.index }}</td>
      <td><code>{{ s.command }}</code></td>
      <td>{{ s.ran_at }}</td>
      <td style="font-size:.78rem; color:#555;">
        {% for k, v in s.params.items() %}
          {% if k != "h5ad" and k != "out_dir" %}
            <span style="margin-right:.6rem;">{{ k }}=<code>{{ v }}</code></span>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>
{% else %}
<p style="color:#999;">No manifest found — was this run-dir produced by scellrun ≥ 0.1.2?</p>
{% endif %}

<h2>Provenance trail</h2>
<div class="provenance">
  Each stage's report carries three tiers of evidence:
  <ul style="margin: .4rem 0 0 1rem;">
    <li><strong>Data</strong> — per-cell metrics, cluster sizes, sample mixing.</li>
    <li><strong>Inference</strong> — opinionated thresholds (with rationale text in each report) and panel matches (with score / margin to runner-up).</li>
    <li><strong>Literature</strong> — when <code>--pubmed</code> is enabled at the annotate stage, top recent PubMed papers per marker.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p style="font-size:.85rem; color:#888; margin-top:2rem;">
  Generated by <code>scellrun report</code>. To export to PDF, open this page in
  a browser and use Print → Save as PDF (Chromium prints these layouts cleanly).
</p>

</body>
</html>
